1286
01:10:58,796 --> 01:11:00,232
It's okay.

1287
01:11:03,569 --> 01:11:05,737
Hmm?

1288
01:11:08,873 --> 01:11:11,808
Tim, look.

1289
01:11:39,605 --> 01:11:40,672
Okay.

1290
01:11:43,175 --> 01:11:44,844
