1291
01:12:20,680 --> 01:12:22,582
You're gonna be okay, partner.

1292
01:13:13,131 --> 01:13:14,366
Here?

1293
01:13:26,177 --> 01:13:27,977
Hey! Wait, wait, wait!

1294
01:13:27,979 --> 01:13:30,080
Where are you going?

1295
01:13:30,082 --> 01:13:32,348
