1296
01:13:32,350 --> 01:13:34,920
I've been waiting for you.

1297
01:13:39,925 --> 01:13:40,927
Mewtwo.

1298
01:13:42,994 --> 01:13:44,995
No, no, no! No, wait!

1299
01:14:03,149 --> 01:14:04,384
Where am I?

