1327
01:16:00,565 --> 01:16:02,632
You wouldn't do that.
I don't care what I saw.

1328
01:16:02,634 --> 01:16:04,500
- I know who you are.
- How do you know?

1329
01:16:04,502 --> 01:16:05,835
Because, I...

1330
01:16:05,837 --> 01:16:07,571
