what we found.

1361
01:17:23,114 --> 01:17:24,248
This is breaking news.

1362
01:17:24,250 --> 01:17:26,517
No. No, you should
break the news. You.

1363
01:17:26,519 --> 01:17:28,184
I'm gonna go talk to Howard.

1364
01:17:28,186 --> 01:17:29,585
How...

1365
01:17:29,587 --> 01:17:30,853
